text: Appears that this product is well constructed and will fit the bill. Delivery period should have been half the time demonstrated as in doing processes I need quick responses. A week for a small device posted anywhere in the USA to another USA state (CONUS) should be no longer than 3 days including ordering by 3 PM local.
